":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"TF cost/2 = 兩支Dirac delta function 一支 1/2 一支-1/2<br />\n<br />\n反轉shift 去到-3/2 一支overlap 左個x(jw)出<br />\n<br />\n所以有左邊既三角形<br />\n<br />\n一路shift <br />\n<br />\n後面果支開始overlap 個向左邊既三角形 前一支又開始<br />\n<br />\nOverlap 右邊既三角形 所以就平左<br />\n<br />\n最尾後面果支overlap 右邊三角形"},{"pid":"9f2616edf04d88987a108953eab5b98205f948c1","tid":940040,"uid":193609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"多謝上面兩位巴打，而家有d急事忙緊<br />\n一陣即睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c358126474488ff5c58764ec30e331f3ada908","tid":940040,"uid":193609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f346926f4ef1b73dd220633d261e7ff655f9e7c8","tid":940040,"uid":217096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"y(t)=x(t)p(t) <br />\nFrequency domain 係 y(jw)=x(jw)*p(jw)<br />\nwhere * is convolution<br />\ncos(t) FT 後 個spectrum 係 -1 1 兩支impulse<br />\ncos(t/2) FT 後 個spectrum 係 -0.5 0.5 兩支impulse<br />\n<br />\n反轉個x(jw) 掃過去即成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"出兩枝impulse個度都明<br />\n<br />\n反轉個x(jw) 掃過去即成<br />\n但想問呢句點解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca040687f78e2890c1ca767030d27053752ae73a","tid":940040,"uid":193609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T18:37:00.000Z","msg":"明咗啦<br />\n唔該哂上面兩位巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}